{"tid":90584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分享比香港寬頻用財仔收數經歷","createTime":"2017-01-22T08:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T11:30:20.000Z","uid":74302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5b367b7d71da0d2a65be15dcbe78fc113da5238","tid":90584,"uid":74302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:19:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的。上年我老母頂唔順和記offer  搵左香港寬頻做新客。半年前就比條sales chur 安裝定先。後來我媽決定都係續約。就取消左香港寬頻。因為佢地有提供考慮期比我地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後來取消左新客申請。個垃圾寬頻狗照交張單上去（事後先知）。但冇月費單寄過來。申請人電話改左一個數字<br />\n半年後寄律師信要我地交600蚊<br />\n後來我地以為係一開始安裝費。比左佢地算。點撚知仲有收數佬恐嚇我老母話差幾千蚊<br />\n<br />\n我即時火都來查好哂條例同電信管理局既野起埋草稿。再打上去屌佢地。佢地話會查。我就話咁可唔可以唔好再搵收數佬騷擾我老母呢？ <br />\n佢就話呢方面係財務部既決定來.....<br />\n<br />\n過幾日就打來話佢地搞錯左。對唔住喎<br />\n我果時忙緊。只係醒起叫佢地退番我老母比果六百蚊。冇再要求咩賠償<br />\n<br />\n心諗呢間垃圾 同寬頻狗sales. 可恥。交唔到數關人撚窮咩。香港寬頻阿Ben<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549ab53cae96f91bc2f97c1192f6cfe1b5b9304f","tid":90584,"uid":15693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:22:12.000Z","msg":"安裝左就要比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa54ab71b00209ee97722663a091a043e55452fc","tid":90584,"uid":74302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>安裝左就要比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n合約仲有半年先啟動。三個月冷靜期本身話<br />\n冷靜期完前取消左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n照收錢"},{"pid":"b15e65315c26587daf3aa8db012209b1f5eeac6e","tid":90584,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"點解肯俾$600?"},{"pid":"1df2f5d490317de6b8bcb5086b9244a4671d962a","tid":90584,"uid":74302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解肯俾$600?</blockquote><br />\n因為用律師信嚇到我老母煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔知原來係月費"},{"pid":"16e5ffb5321d3b51fcfedc6a1c670a5b2d31cc31","tid":90584,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解肯俾$600?</blockquote><br />\n因為用律師信嚇到我老母煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔知原來係月費</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCall Apple daily"},{"pid":"47ab7c0a886fab553a5ef83b49a7a3fc266a7ba5","tid":90584,"uid":14013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"Hkbn狗都唔撚用喇屌<br />\n<br />\n當舊客係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n貴撚過新客多多聲<br />\n<br />\n又成撚日亂收錢，簽果陣又唔撚講"},{"pid":"74e0c3dc052b22d8bd2a6f73e8fe4deec9754ce5","tid":90584,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:10:18.000Z","msg":"搞大佢搵Apple daily,消委會"},{"pid":"b7fbb52825ff112500632c7f65b0c51aa37d096e","tid":90584,"uid":74302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"件事都過左半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  當時冇諗到搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0f9eb02f02883e5908a225e49b4d5135e43192","tid":90584,"uid":74302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T11:30:20.000Z","msg":"只係準備寄野去電信管理局。未寄佢就處理完"}]}